subtests.name: 'rotate(acos(0))' as a specified value should serialize as 'rotate(calc(90deg))'.
'rotate(acos(0))' as a computed value should serialize as 'matrix(0, 1, -1, 0, 0, 0)'.
'rotate(asin(1))' as a specified value should serialize as 'rotate(calc(90deg))'.
'rotate(asin(1))' as a computed value should serialize as 'matrix(0, 1, -1, 0, 0, 0)'.
'rotate(calc(acos(pi - pi)))' as a specified value should serialize as 'rotate(calc(90deg))'.
'rotate(calc(acos(pi - pi)))' as a computed value should serialize as 'matrix(0, 1, -1, 0, 0, 0)'.
'rotate(calc(asin(pi - pi + 1)))' as a specified value should serialize as 'rotate(calc(90deg))'.
'rotate(calc(asin(pi - pi + 1)))' as a computed value should serialize as 'matrix(0, 1, -1, 0, 0, 0)'.
